snippet.title: Dark Fracture - Exclusive Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Check out the trailer for the psychological horror adventure game Dark Fracture. Step into the shoes of a man grappling with his inner demons while exploring an eerie body farm, solving puzzles, and facing otherworldly horrors. Dark Fracture is launching on PC in 2024.
